eelchairs%20for%20dogs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-300x171.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-500x285.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-768x438.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-1536x876.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-150x86.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339849%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERajiv%20made%20%E2%80%98wheelchairs%E2%80%99%20for%20dogs%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20rescue%20cows%20and%20bulls.%20When%20they%20were%20operated%20upon%2C%20veterinarians%20found%20plastic%20in%20their%20stomachs%2C%20which%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20digest.%20I%20have%20been%20against%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fauthor%2Fsowmyamani%2Fpage%2F3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20that%20day.%20Our%20fresheners%20too%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20plastic%20in%20them.%20Just%20put%20our%20device%20in%20your%20garden%20after%20use%20and%20it%20will%20get%20composted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunning%20the%20startup%20from%20his%20home%20currently%2C%20Rajiv%20hopes%20to%20expand%20soon.%20ALVE%20Green%20Solutions%20has%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Bangalore%2C%20where%20five%20college%20students%20will%20be%20working%20with%20the%20startup%20to%20develop%20the%20product.%20The%20air%20fresheners%20are%20currently%20being%20sold%20offline%2C%20at%20events%2C%20and%20through%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CALVE%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20Alveoli%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20sac-like%20structure%20present%20in%20our%20lungs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20exchange%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20and%20oxygen.%20Without%20this%20organ%2C%20the%20body%20fails%20to%20survive%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20a%20most%20important%20part%20of%20our%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20he%20wants%20ALVE%20to%20be%20an%20important%20part%20of%20each%20home%20for%20healthier%20living.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20create%20products%20that%20not%20only%20meet%20human%20needs%20but%20also%20leave%20a%20positive%20imprint%20on%20our%20planet.%20Our%20vision%20at%20ALVE%20is%20to%20inspire%20a%20world%20where%20fresh%2C%20clean%20air%20is%20not%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20sustainable%20standard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706192933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20ecofriendly%20air%20fresheners%3F%20Jamshedpur's%20Rajiv%20Sharma%20innovated%20ALVE%20smart%20air%20fresheners%20by%20recycling%201500%20kgs%20of%20temple%20flower%20waste.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%20'appalled'%20by%20reported%20criticism%20from%20Israel's%20Netanyahu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706192932000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA1D8%2Fproduction%2F_132423414_68481a353af5fe8b9395620b73b0684a5c1ffc56.j