%20are%20the%20highlight%20of%20my%20kids'%20school%20days.%20Warm%2C%20healthy%20meals%20with%20multiple%20side%20dishes%20like%20fresh%20salads%2C%20crab%20soup%2C%20duck%2C%20and%20shrimp%20cakes%20with%20macarons%20for%20dessert.%20No%20child%20ever%20brings%20a%20lunch%20box%20to%20school%20%E2%80%94%20nothing%20to%20pack%20except%20for%20field%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShuttle%20services%20for%20after-school%20programs%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20kids%20to%20participate%20in%20activities.%20Schools%20also%20offer%20many%20programs%2C%20including%20robotics%2C%20piano%2C%20martial%20arts%2C%20coding%2C%20soccer%2C%20art%2C%20and%20academic%20subjects.%20Multicultural%20families%20have%20access%20to%20private%20tutoring%20for%20language%2C%20math%2C%20and%20life%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20send%20our%20youngest%20to%20full-time%20day%20care%20and%20pay%20only%20our%20low%20school%20taxes.%20Preschool%20education%20offers%20a%20blended%20Montessori%20approach%20with%20modern%20facilities%2C%20including%20swimming%20pools%20and%20vegetable%20gardens.%20Our%20boys%20enjoy%20their%20educational%20experiences.%20As%20they%20get%20older%2C%20they%20benefit%20from%20public%20International%20Baccalaureate%20schools%2C%20which%20aim%20to%20create%20communicative%20and%20self-directed%20learners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20South%20Korea%2C%20we%20have%20discovered%20a%20community%20where%20all%20children%20can%20flourish%2C%20that%20celebrates%20multiculturalism%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20starred%20in%20television%20shows%2C%20performances%2C%20and%20books%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20educating%20kids%20is%20a%20unique%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20continue%20to%20embrace%20the%20educational%20opportunities%2C%20the%20culture%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20delicious%20food%20South%20Korea%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-benefits-raising-kids-tax-cred