ar-sales-plateau-early-adopters-competition-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20car-curious%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20customers%20who%20created%20the%20initial%20EV%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20GBK%20President%20Jeremy%20Korst%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20EV%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcar-buyer-interest-hybrids-as-electric-vehicle-adoption-slowing-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20considerers%3C%2Fa%3E%20landed%20much%20further%20down%20on%20the%20technology%20adoption%20curve%20than%20the%20EV%20owners%2C%20and%20are%20often%20shopping%20green%20options%20against%20gas-powered%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20later%20adopters%2C%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20they're%20not%20as%20driven%20by%20innovation%20or%20even%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20Korst%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20more%20functional%20needs%2C%20and%20they're%20much%20more%20pragmatic%20and%20thinking%20about%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20ownership%20both%20in%20price%20and%20in%20effort%2C%20like%2C%20'how%20do%20I%20charge%20so%20what's%20that%20going%20to%20take%3F%20How%20much%20time%20is%20it%20going%20to%20take%20me%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGBK's%20findings%20back%20up%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-sales-getting-tougher-car-dealers-say-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecar%20dealers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20industry%20experts%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautomakers-over-estimated-electric-vehicle-demand-early-adopters-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etelling%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20last%20several%20months.%20A%20new%20wave%20of%20EV%20shoppers%20is%20hitting%20the%20market%2C%20and%20the%20industry%20appears%20to%20be%20unprepared%20to%20meet%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EToyota%20could%20win%20over%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20EV%20shoppers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20wave%20of%20EV%20shoppers%20has%20a%20median%20budget%20of%20%2450%2C000%20for%20their%20next%20vehicle%2C%20compared%20to%20an%20average%20budget%20of%20%2459%2C000%20for%20current%20EV%20owners%2C%20GBK's%20study%20found.%20These%20shoppers%20also%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectrc-vehicle-demand-problem-affordability-expense-price-cost-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20priorities%20than%20current%20EV%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20next%20vehicles%2C%20putting%20more%20weight%20on%20environmental%20impact%20and%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20budget-minded%20shoppers%20are%20also%20more%20partial%20to%20legacy%20car%20brands%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-q4-sales-less-than-china-byd-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknocking%20Tesla%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20rankings%20for%20consideration%20among%20this%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20group%20of%20EV%20considerers%20surveyed%2C%20Toyota%20was%20the%20most%20considered%20brand%2C%20with%2047%25%20showing%20a%20preference%20for%20the%20Japanese%20automaker%20compared%20to%2041%25%20favoring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-elon-musk-acted-normal-this-year-it-worked-out-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Tesla.%20In%20third%20place%20was%20Ford%2C%20which%20has%20amped%20up%20its%20EV%20offerings%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20another%20sign%20that%20a%20more%20pragmatic%20buyer%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20EV%20segment%2C%20Korst%20said.%20Toyota's%20more%20hybrid-heavy%20approach%20to%20electric%20cars%20speaks%20more%20directly%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-buying-hybrids-as-electric-vehicle-sales-growth-