2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe%20took%20me%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20his%20life%20in%20the%20Bronx%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20after%20his%2090th%20birthday%2C%20a%20celebration%20filled%20with%20gourmet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-city-famous-pastrami-sandwich-katzs-delicatessen-review-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York-style%20deli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20egg%20creams%20stirred%20meticulously%20by%20Aunt%20Mary%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20my%20father%20and%20where%20he%20came%20from.%20While%20my%20mother%20spoke%20endlessly%20of%20her%20family%20and%20her%20past%2C%20my%20father%20barely%20mentioned%20a%20word.%20This%20time%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20it%20was%20like%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20Bronx.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I'll%20show%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20he%20took%20out%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20paper%20where%20he%20etched%20three%20of%20his%20previous%20addresses%20on.%20As%20he%20unfolded%20them%2C%20we%20placed%20each%20one%20into%20the%20phone%20and%20began%20our%20journey%20in%20his%20Camry.%20No%2C%20his%20memory%20wasn't%20that%20precise%2C%20but%20he%20did%2C%20however%2C%20recall%20an%20application%20he%20filled%20out%20for%20the%20military%20that%20listed%20his%20old%20addresses%2C%20and%20this%20we%20began%20our%20journey.%20He%20drove%2C%20of%20course.%20Cutting%20corners%2C%20making%20U-turns%2C%20squeezing%20into%20parking%20spots%2C%20all%20with%20a%20city%20precision%20I%20have%20yet%20to%20master.%20We%20arrived%20at%20each%20spot%2C%20where%20we%20walked%20over%20broken%20glass%20and%20bottles%20to%20tall%20apartments%2C%20sometimes%20abandoned%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20one%20we%20lived%20in%2C%20then%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20we%20moved%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20buildings%20with%20the%20only%20view%20being%20the%20Cross%20Bronx%20Expressway.%