3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20Muslims%20constitute%20one%20of%20the%20most%20marginalised%20social%20groups.%20Besides%20being%20looked%20down%20with%20condescension%20as%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20are%20stereotyped%20as%20%E2%80%9CBangladeshi%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrant%E2%80%9D%20and%20even%20%E2%80%9CJihadi%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20citizenship%20is%20persistently%20under%20attack%2C%20and%20they%20are%20targeted%20through%20the%20state%20power%20through%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%2C%20and%20issues%20such%20as%20eviction%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20voters%E2%80%9D.%20A%20lot%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20against%20Assam%20Muslims%20are%20already%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20In%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20specifically%20deal%20with%20the%20question%20of%20representation%20vis-a-vis%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20of%20Assam%20are%20a%20heterogeneous%20category%2C%20who%20are%20sub-divided%20into%20Miya%20Muslims%2C%20Goriya%2C%20Moria%2C%20Julha%2C%20Deshi%2C%20Bihari%20Muslims%2C%20Muslims%20of%20Barak%20Valley%2C%20etc.%20The%20ruling%20parties%20in%20the%20state%20have%20been%20sharpening%20the%20existing%20faultlines%20amongst%20Muslim%20groups%20in%20the%20state.%20Some%20Muslim%20groups%20like%20Goriya%2C%20Moria%2C%20Julha%2C%20Deshi%2C%20Syed%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20arbitrarily%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20only%20to%20exclude%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%20from%20the%20public%20and%20political%20spheres.%20Miya%20Muslims%20are%20arguably%20the%20most%20discriminated%20and%20excluded%20category%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20in%20this%20article%2C%20I%20will%20briefly%20discuss%20the%20total%20discrimination%20against%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20in%20general%2C%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20question%20of%20representation%20of%20the%20community%20in%20the%20major%20public%20institutions%2C%20on%20which%20the%20government%20is%20clearly%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdetention-criminalisation-statelessness-the-aftermath-of-assams-nrc%5C%22%3EDetention%2C%20Criminalisation%2C%20Statelessness%3A%20The%20Aftermath%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20NRC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbysmal%20representation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20about%2035%25%20Muslim%20population%2C%20and%20the%20representation%20of%20this%20community%20in%20government%20offices%20is%20abysmally%20low.%20Presently%2C%20there%20are%2016%20ministers%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20and%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20state%20has%2034%20districts%20and%20not%20even%20a%20single%20district%20has%20a%20Muslim%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC).%20In%20these%2034%20districts%2C%20not%20even%20a%20single%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fghconline.gov.in%2Findex.php%2Fhonble-the-chief-justice-sitting-judges%2F%5C%22%3EGauhati%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%2023%20judges%2C%20including%20one%20chief%20justice%C2%A0and%20surprisingly%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20These%20discriminations%20are%20not%20only%20limited%20to%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20after%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20state%20has%2031%20Muslim%20MLAs%20out%20of%20126%20MLAs.%20The%20share%20amounts%20to%2024.60%25%20of%20the%20total%20MLAs.%20But%20a%20proportionate%20number%20would%20be%2043%20Muslim%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Assam%20state%20assembly.%20In%20the%202016%20assembly%20elections%2C%2029%20Muslim%20MLAs%20were%20elected%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%2023.02%25%20representation.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%2C%20at%20least%20none%20Muslim%20MLA%20seats%20will%20be%20further%20lost%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20election.%20The%20state%20presently%20has%20two%20Muslim%20MPs%20out%20of%2014%20MPs%2C%20meaning%20only%2014.29%25%20Muslim%20representation%20among%20the%20MPs.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20the%20number%20of%20MPs%2C%20which%20will%20be%20representative%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-578102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20has%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhighereducation.assam.gov.in%2Fportlets%2Fprofiles-of-universities-and-colleges%5C%22%3Ecentral%20universities%20and%2014%20state%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20taken%20a%20sample%20of%20five%20universities%20to%20see%20the%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20teaching%20positions%20from%20their%20respective%20website%2C%20in%20these%20universities.%20One%20of%20these%20universities%20is%20a%20central%20university%20(Tezpur%20University)%2C%20and%20the%20other%20four%20are%20state%20universities.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20state%20universities%2C%20I%20have%20included%20one%20recently%20opened%20university%20(BSSR%20University)%20and%20the%20oldest%20university%20in%20the%20region%20(Gauhati%20University).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETezpur%20Central%20University%20has%20a%20representation%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%203.98%25%2C%20while%20Gauhati%20University%20has%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%207.47%25.%20Arabic%20and%20Parsi%20departments%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20University%20alone%20have%20seven%20Muslim%20teachers%2C%20and%20without%20these%20two%20departments%2C%20the%20representation%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20in%20the%20University%20comes%20down%20to%205.54%25.%20Bodoland%20University%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%20(BTR)%20of%20Assam%2C%20does%20not%20have%20a%20single%20Muslim%20teacher%20out%20of%20the%2093%20teachers%20the%20university%20has.%20Another%20relatively%20old%20university%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Dibrugarh%20University%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%201965%2C%20has%20about%202.44%25%20of%20its%20teachers%20Muslim%2C%20which%20is%20abysmally%20low.%20BSSR%20Vishwavidyalaya%20is%20a%20newly%20opened%20university%20in%20the%20Golaghat%20district%20of%20the%20state%20with%205.88%25%20of%20Muslim%20teachers.%20All%20these%20clearly%20show%20severely%20less%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20university%20system%20than%20their%20population%20share%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20about%2035%25.%20Representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20media%20houses%20in%20the%20state%20is%20either%20abysmally%20low%20or%20entirely%20missing.%20This%20underrepresentation%20is%20not%20an%20overnight%20phenomenon%2C%20for%20it%20happened%20over%20the%20decades%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESl.%20No.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EName%20of%20the%20University%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20number%20of%20teachers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%20(Permanent%20positions)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPercentage%20of%20Muslim%20teachers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E01.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EGauhati%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E361%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E27%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E7.47%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E02.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EBodoland%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E93%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E0%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E0%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E03.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EBSSR%20Vishwavidyalaya%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E17%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E01%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E5.88%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E04.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3ETezpur%20Central%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E276%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E11%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E3.98%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E05.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%3EDibrugarh%20University%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E286%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22125%5C%22%3E07%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22108%5C%22%3E2.44%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%20Websites%20of%20the%20respective%C2%A0%20university%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0current%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20meant%20for%20the%20poor%20also%20exclude%20Muslims.%20A%20recent%20example%20is%20a%20scheme%2C%20namely%20Mukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Udyamita%20Abhiyaan%20(MMUA)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20scheme%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20to%20improve%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20rural%20women.%20To%20benefit%20from%20this%20scheme%2C%20women%20cannot%20have%20more%20than%20three%20children%20except%20in%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC).%20Women%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20categories%20can%20benefit%20from%20this%20scheme%20even%20if%20they%20have%20four%20children.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Sachar%20committee%20clarifies%20that%20the%20economic%20condition%20of%20Muslims%20is%20worse%20than%20that%20of%20SCs%20and%20STs.%20And%20in%20a%20time%20when%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20have%20more%20children%2C%20it%20is%20the%20poorest%20sections%20of%20all%20communities%20that%20have%20relatively%20more%20children.%20Mary%20E%20John%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fassam-government-new-schemes-discrimination-communalisation-not-justice-9111255%2F%5C%22%3Ecritiques%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20move%20of%20the%20government%20and%20argues%20that%20this%20scheme%20is%20to%20exclude%20Muslim%20women%20who%20are%20more%20marginalised.%C2%A0%20Another%20scheme%2C%20namely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-chief-minister-is-communalising-land-settlement-scheme-aiudf%2Farticle66144465.ece%5C%22%3EVasundhara%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20through%20which%20land%20rights%20are%20given%20to%20landless%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%20too%20excludes%20Muslims%20totally.%20There%20are%20many%20such%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Overwhelming%20number%20of%20Muslims%20as%20undertrials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20jails%20of%20the%20state%20throws%20a%20very%20interesting%20picture.%20As%20per%20Prison%20Statistics%20India%202022%2C%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Crimes%20Record%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%2055.6%25%20of%20convicts%20lodged%20in%20the%20prisons%20of%20Assam%20are%20Muslims.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20undertrials%20lodged%20in%20the%20jails%2C%2052.54%25%20of%20them%20are%20Muslims%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20above%20discussion%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20discrimination%20and%20exclusion%20are%20visible%20in%20Assam.%20Muslims%20in%20Assam%20are%20excluded%20from%20decision-making%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20various%20institutions%2C%20including%20institutions%20of%20higher%20learning%20and%20administration.%20They%20are%20purposely%20and%20systematically%20made%20voiceless%20regarding%20policy%20formation%20and%20problem-raising.%20An%20exhaustive%20study%20to%20understand%20the%20discrimination%20and%20underrepresentation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20public%20life%20in%20the%20state%20is%20the%20urgent%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20The%20situation%20is%20all%20the%20more%20alarming%20as%20Abdur%20Rahman%20writes%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EAbsent%20in%20Politics%20and%20Power%2C%20Political%20Exclusion%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20openly%20portrays%20itself%20as%20anti-Muslim%20and%20has%20been%20against%20all%20forms%20of%20their%20empowerment.%20By%20depriving%20them%20of%20a%20just%20and%20equitable%20share%20in%20education%2C%20economy%20and%20politics%2C%20the%20party%20intends%20to%20push%20them%20into%20becoming%20second%20class%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20(p.97).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20word%20discrimination%20is%20meaningless%20if%20the%20discrimination%20against%20Muslims%20is%20not%20considered.%20While%20other%20discriminated%20social%20groups%20enjoy%20the%20benefit%20of%20reservation%2C%20most%20of%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%20of%20the%20state%2C%20do%20not%20have%20any%20reservation%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20system.%20They%20are%20always%20pushed%20to%20the%20margin%20to%20struggle%20for%20basic%20survival%20%E2%80%93%20food%2C%20clothes%2C%20and%20land.%20The%20picture%20of%20missing%20Muslims%20from%20public%20institutions%20is%20completely%20contradictory%20to%20the%20claim%2C%20%3Cem%3Esabke%20saath%20sabka%20bikas%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20a%20community%20away%20from%20the%20positions%20of%20power%20in%20government-run%20institutions%20leads%20to%20stereotyping%20of%20the%20community.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20to%20bring%20Muslims%20of%20Assam%20into%20a%20suitable%20reservation%20system%20in%20the%20line%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20to%20ensure%20proportionate%20representation%20of%20this%20community%20in%20the%20social%2C%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20educational%20positions%20and%20to%20ensure%20social%20justice%20to%20this%20marginalised%20community.%20The%20constitution%20of%20India%20promised%20equal%20opportunity%20for%20all%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20citizens%2C%20and%20it%20is%20time%20to%20deliver%20this%20promise%20to%20these%20marginalised%20citizens%20of%20peripheral%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENazimuddin%20Siddique%20teaches%20Sociology%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%20sid.nazimuddin%40gmail.com.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706183199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F21151635%2FScreen-Shot-2021-06-21-at-3.16.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muslims%2C%20who%20constitute%2035%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20are%20abysmally%20represented%20in%20the%20positions%20of%20power.%20Their%20share%2C%20however%2C%20among%20the%20undertrials%20in%20the%20state%20in%2052.54%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%22%2C%22cdnA