ar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20bloc%20appears%20to%20be%20unravelling%20as%20a%20third%20key%20leader%20--%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20--%20is%20likely%20to%20change%20camp%20again.%20Sources%20said%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20in%20a%20last-minute%20U-turn%20will%20partner%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-may-exit-alliance-in-bihar-likely-to-go-with-bjp-again-sources-4929675%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Ally%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Won't%20Join%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%20In%20Bihar%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20will%20not%20join%20the%20Congress'%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20when%20it%20enters%20his%20state%20on%20January%2030%2C%20sources%20said%20Thursday%20afternoon.%20Sources%20said%20an%20invitation%20was%20extended%20last%20evening%20-%20via%20the%20Congress'%20legislature%20party%20leader%20Shakeel%20Ahmad%20Khan%20but%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20already%20upset%20by%20delays%20to%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20was%20non-committal%20about%20his%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snub%20comes%20three%20days%20after%20the%20Congress'%20Bihar%20unit%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20%26quot%3Bhad%20agreed%26quot%3B%20to%20appear%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Purnia%20district.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20event%20of%20his%20getting%20caught%20elsewhere%2C%20