%2C%22author%22%3A%22AABHAS%20SHARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2F40-years-of-mac-an-evolution-and-a-revolution-that-changed-your-pc-forever%2Farticleshow%2F107146648.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ladakh%3A%20Renaming%20Govt%20Health%20Centres%20'Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs'%20Invites%20Backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163733%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-25-at-2.06.02-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20rename%20the%20health%20centres%20as%20%E2%80%9CAyushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs%E2%80%9D%20has%20stirred%20a%20fierce%20controversy%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20with%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20most%20influential%20Buddhist%20organisation%20and%20elected%20representatives%20calling%20this%20an%20affront%20to%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20living%20in%20the%20two-district%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecision%2C%20controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%20decided%20to%20rename%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Wellness%20Centres%20(AB-HWCs)%20as%20%E2%80%98Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20tag%20line%20%E2%80%98Arogyam%20Parmam%20Dhanam%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20wrote%20to%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20November%2025%2C%202023%20to%20implement%20the%20rebranding%20exercise%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20submit%20photographs%20of%20these%20health%20facilities%20with%20the%20new%20title%20by%20December%2031%2C%202023.%20It%20even%20earmarked%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20facility%20for%20this%20rebranding%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20decision%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20especially%20in%20Buddhist-majority%20Leh%20district%2C%20where%20a%20prominent%20religious%20group%20has%20taken%20strong%20objection%20to%20it%20and%20written%20to%20the%20elected%20bodies%20of%20the%20region%20to%20raise%20their%20concerns%20with%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20over%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20order%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20renaming%20the%20Govt.%20medical%20aid%20centers%2F%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%20centers%20as%20%E2%80%9CAyushman%20Arogya%20Mandir%E2%80%99%20is%20unfortunate%20and%20tantamount%20to%20playing%20with%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chering%20Dorjey%20Lakrook%2C%20acting%20president%2C%20Ladakh%20Buddhist%20Association%20(LBA)%20wrote%20to%20the%20chief%20executive%20councilors%20of%20the%20Hill%20Councils%20of%20both%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LBA%20has%20asked%20heads%20of%20both%20the%20elected%20bodies%20to%20get%20the%20decision%20rescinded.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20using%20religious%20names%20and%20symbols%20in%20government%20departments%20is%20unconstitutional%20and%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dorjay%20said%2C%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dorjay%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party-BJP%20government%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20said%20that%20this%20decision%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20us.%20What%20is%20the%20fun%20of%20naming%20hospitals%20as%20mandirs%3F%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20steps%20towards%20making%20India%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LBA%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20religious%20group%20in%20Buddhist-dominated%20Leh%20and%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20guardian%20of%20Buddhist%20identity%20in%20the%20region.%20It%20has%20considerable%20influence%20on%20social%20and%20political%20matters%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25163841%2Fcollage-AAM-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694390%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERebranded%20health%20centres%20in%20Ladakh.%20Photos%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rechristening%20of%20health%20centres%20has%20also%20evoked%20criticism%20from%20elected%20representatives%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20councillors%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Council-Leh%20have%20written%20to%20the%20CECs%20of%20both%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20that%20people%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20have%20been%20hurt%20by%20the%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20decision%20might%20become%20a%20hindrance%20to%20health%20centres%20being%20universally%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20letter%20signed%20by%2010%20councilors%20of%20the%20Hill%20Council%2C%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20religious%20and%20cultural%20sentiments%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20they%20have%20also%20urged%20the%20CECs%20to%20get%20the%20decision%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmanla%20Dorje%20Nurboo%2C%20councilor%20Saspol%20constituency%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20people%20are%20offended%20by%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20health%20facilities%20should%20be%20accessible%20to%20everyone%20but%20this%20move%20will%20create%20hindrances%20in%20accessing%20these%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Smanla%2C%20who%20is%20also%20president%20of%20Youth%20Congress%20in%20Ladakh%20UT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20blames%20local%20authorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20damage-control%20exercise%2C%20CEC%2C%20LAHDC-Leh%2C%20Tashi%20Gaylson%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20written%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20B.D.%20Mishra%20to%20express%20his%20concern%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20said%2C%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20that%20the%20move%20has%20generated%20significant%20resentment%20among%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%2C%20however%2C%20put%20the%20blame%20on%20officials%20from%20the%20Ladakh%20health%20department%20for%20the%20controversy%2C%20saying%20they%20could%20have%20translated%20the%20title%20into%20the%20state%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20handout%2C%20the%20CEC%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CGoI%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20offend%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20as%20the%20order%20clearly%20stipulated%20that%20the%20full%20and%20exact%20title%20could%20be%20translated%20into%20the%20state%20language%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20health%20department%20overlooked%20the%20directive%20and%20opted%20for%20the%20easiest%20path%20without%20considering%20the%20potential%20negative%20impact%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20has%20erupted%20at%20a%20time%20when%20two%20prominent%20groups%20of%20Ladakh%20are%20involved%20in%20parleys%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20seek%20safe