%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereligious%20faith%2C%C2%A0%20while%C2%A0%20respecting%20%C2%A0the%C2%A0%20freedom%20of%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eall%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0faiths%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprofess%2C%20practice%2C%20and%20propagate%E2%80%9D%20the%20tenets%20of%20their%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20a%20liberal-democratic%20jaw%20now%20hangs%20in%20silent%20consternation%20at%20the%20unrepentant%C2%A0%20brazenness%C2%A0%20of%20the%20proceedings%3B%20but%20they%20may%20have%20only%20themselves%20to%20blame%20for%20having%20believed%20that%20the%20social%2F%20cultural%C2%A0%20right-wing%20would%20never%20find%20the%20purchase%20politically%20to%20unleash%20its%20revanchist%20agenda%20in%20quite%20the%20measure%20now%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20that%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Representation%20Act%20to%20the%20contrary%2C%20unfettered%20denominational%C2%A0%20propagation%20would%20come%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20route%20to%20political%2F%20electoral%C2%A0%20ambitions%2C%20with%20not%20a%20murmur%2C%20(with%20honourable%2C%20even%20if%20beleaguered%2C%C2%A0%20exceptions)%2C%20from%20the%20world%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwatch-dogs%E2%80%9D%2C%20namely%C2%A0%20journalists%2C%20academics%2C%20judges%2C%20not%20to%20speak%20of%20the%20officialdom%20that%20is%20formally%20charged%20with%20ensuring%20the%20compliance%20of%20political%20protagonists%20with%20the%20strict%C2%A0%20injunctions%20of%20electoral%C2%A0%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20was%20it%20anticipated%2C%20over%20all%2C%20that%20liberal%20democracy%20would%20in%20India%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20mere%20elitist%20patina%20over%20a%20%C2%A0dour%20feudal%2Frevanchist%20framework%C2%A0%20firmly%20anchored%20in%20the%20worship%20of%20power%2C%20vested%20be%20it%20among%20men%20or%20deities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20a%20new%20so-called%20apolitical%20(read%20ultra%20conservative)%20class%20of%20Indians%20would%20emerge%20from%20our%20technological%C2%A0%C2%A0%20advance%2C%20and%20seek%20to%20marry%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Ctime-honoured%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0social%2F%20cultural%2F%20religious%20hierarchies%20and%20persuasions%20%C2%A0to%20a%20faceless%20and%20inhuman%20digital%20modernity%20was%20likewise%20%C2%A0not%20in%20%C2%A0the%20minds%20of%C2%A0%20leaderships%20who%20had%20banked%20on%20technological%20advance%20to%20also%20further%20%C2%A0%C2%A0ideological%20emancipation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20it%20be%20said%20that%20even%20Karl%20Marx%20who%20set%20great%20store%20by%20technological%20advance%20as%20a%20force%20of%20production%20did%20not%20foresee%20that%20the%20material%20progress%C2%A0%20enabled%20by%20such%20advance%20would%C2%A0%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20so%20counter-%20productive%20to%C2%A0%20overall%20human%20emancipation%20from%20the%20%C2%A0irrational%20%C2%A0oppressions%20of%20the%20old%20world.%20Or%2C%20indeed%2C%20would%20only%C2%A0%20marry%20those%20oppressions%20to%20%C2%A0technological%20controls%2C%20yielding%20the%20ruthless%20politics%20of%20religio-corporate%20fascism..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20political%20opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20truly%20askance%20at%20the%20unrelenting%20and%20abject%20uniformity%20of%20the%20agenda%20now%20daily%20peddled%20by%20%E2%80%9Cmainstream%E2%80%9D%20media%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20sing%20all-day-and-night-long%20hosannas%20to%20the%20proceedings%20in%20Ayodhya%20temple%20town%2C%20alternated%20with%C2%A0%20ad%20infinitum%20denigrations%20of%20the%20political%20opposition%20for%20being%2C%20allegedly%2C%20merely%20greedy%20on%20behalf%20of%20their%20own%20little%20turfs%2C%20and%20unable%20to%20match%20the%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0towering%20figure%20of%20Shri%20Modi%20who%20%C2%A0commands%20the%20obedience%20and%20supplication%20of%20%C2%A0ostensibly%20an%20entire%20nation%2C%20rendering%20the%20asking%20of%20questions%20both%20superfluous%20and%C2%A0%20unbecoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20behind%20this%20agenda%20and%20persuasion%20lies%20ever-burgeoning%20private%20%C2%A0corporate%20wealth%20is%20by%20now%20acknowledged%20even%20by%20those%20who%20used%20to%20have%20some%20qualms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20state%20institutions%20as%20well%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmainstream%E2%80%9D%20media%2C%20nine%20out%20of%20ten%2C%20finds%20the%20victims%20in%20the%20wrong%20%C2%A0rather%20than%20the%20%C2%A0shamelessly%20%C2%A0partial%20agencies%20who%20tailor%20investigative%20energies%20to%20suit%20the%C2%A0%20faces%20they%C2%A0%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20context%2C%20the%20political%20opposition%2C%20their%20sound%20bytes%20notwithstanding%2C%20do%20seem%20insufficiently%20cognizant%20of%20the%20peril%20that%20awaits%20the%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20in%20the%20dispersed%20opposition%20%C2%A0actually%20seem%20to%20%C2%A0%C2%A0embrace%20the%20%C2%A0likelihood%20outlined%20above%2C%20namely%20that%20losing%20the%20next%20general%20election%C2%A0%20may%20not%20be%20just%20another%20normative%20electoral%20%C2%A0happening%2C%20but%20one%20%C2%A0that%20may%20in%20double%20quick%20time%20lead%20to%20a%20formal%20jettisoning%20of%20the%20basic%20verities%20of%20the%20Constitution%20with%20all%20the%20consequences%20that%20must%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20well%20to%20recognise%20that%20the%20bulk%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20elite%20will%20have%20few%20qualms%20should%20such%20a%20transformation%20be%20attempted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20they%20may%20applaud%20the%20deed%20to%20the%20echo%20which%20will%20applaud%20back%20(to%20borrow%20from%20the%20Bard).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20always%20the%20downtrodden%20who%20have%20the%20highest%20stake%20in%20an%20emancipatory%20constitutional%20order%2C%20and%20in%20a%20fair%20application%20of%20the%20regime%20of%20laws%2C%20not%20having%20friendly%C2%A0access%20to%20centres%20of%20entrenched%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20so%2C%20the%20opposition%20might%20do%20well%C