0for%20him%20around%20that%20would%20be%20to%20take%20up%20his%20end%20of%20the%20bargain%20in%20that%20space%20and%20take%20care%20of%20himself.%26quot%3B%20Maxwell%20was%20rested%20for%20next%20month's%20three-match%20ODI%20series%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20at%20home%20and%20he%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attend%20a%20golf%20event%20in%20Adelaide%20before%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20see%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20playing%20cricket%20for%20the%20next%20three%20to%20four%20years%20for%20Australia.%20Can%20he%20get%20to%20the%20next%20World%20Cup%20in%202027%20in%20South%20Africa%3F%20Who%20knows.%20But%2C%20he's%20a%20key%20player%20in%20our%20white-ball%20formats%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonald%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20is%20out%20there%20we're%20a%20far%20better%20team%2C%20and%20on%20the%20back%20of%20that%20horrific%20injury%20that%20he%20did%20have%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20some%20management%20things%20that%20are%20put%20in%20place%20around%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20we%20want%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20playing%20for%20Australia%20for%20as%20long%20as%20he%20can.%20We're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20do%20our%20end%2C%20and%20Glenn%20is%20no%20doubt%20going%20to%20have%20to%20hold%20up%20his%20end%20of%20the%20bargain.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Maxwell%20has%20been%20in%20trouble.%20In%202022%20after%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Maxwell%20had%20fractured%20his%20leg%20badly%20while%20partying%20at%20a%20friend's%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20kept%20Maxwell%20out%20of%20the%20Australian%20team%20for%20months.%20He%20had%20also%20hurt%20his%20head%20and%20got%20bruises%20after%20falling%20from%20the%20back%20of%20a%20golf%20cart%20in%20a%20freak%20accident%20last%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20information%20he's%20given%2C%20he's%20had%20a%20few%20drinks%2C%20and%20clearly%20the%20night%20has%20ended%20the%20way%20that%20it%20did%2C%20and%20that's%20less%20than%20ideal%20from%20his%20perspective%20and%20our%20perspective.%20It's%20an%20honest%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20McDonald.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20needs%20to%20obviously%20have%20a%20look%20at%20what%20he's%20doing%20at%20his%20end%20and%20is%20that%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20be%20doing%20at%20that%20time%3F%20Thankfully%2C%20there's%20no%20harm%20out%20of%20it.%20He's%20well%20now.%26quot%3B%20Maxwell%20is%20yet%20to%20play%20limited-overs%20cricket%20for%20Australia%20following%20his%20side's%20return%20from%20India%20last%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20finished%20as%20the%20third-highest%20run-scorer%20for%20the%20Australians%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%2C%20which%20they%20won%20for%20the%20record-extending%20sixth%20time%2C%20Maxwell%20participated%20in%20a%20three-match%20T20I%20series%20in%20India%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Big%20Bash%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20finished%20as%20the%20second-highest%20run-scorer%20for%20the%20Stars%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20his%20formidable%20form%20during%20the%20West%20Indies%20T20Is%20from%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706180160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpn2274so_maxwell_625x300_25_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fglenn-maxwell-hospitalised-after-getting-drunk-australia-coach-issues-stern-statement-4923784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20week%20Maxwell%20was%20hospitalised%20in%20Adelaide%20after%20he%20got%20too%20drunk%20after%20attending%20a%20concert%20by%20'Six%20and%20Out'%2C%20the%20band%20featuring%20former%20Australian%20pacer%20Brett%20Lee%20and%20passed%20out%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Kohli%20fan%20invades%20pitch%2C%20touches%20Rohit's%20feet%22%2C%22content%2