is%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20Maoist-affected%20regions%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%20Polling%20booths%20in%20Elmagonda%2C%20Tarrem%2C%20Silger%2C%20and%20Minpa%20were%20set%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20around%203%20decades.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20in%202018%2C%20primary%20schools%20that%20had%20been%20demolished%20were%20re-opened%20in%20collaboration%20with%20community%20members%20and%20the%20district%20administration%20of%20these%20villages%20along%20with%2089%20other%20schools%20in%20utterly%20sensitive%20regions%20of%20the%20constituency.%20These%20schools%20further%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20health%20care%20services%20to%20reach%20these%20villages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Adivasis%20community%20also%20frequently%20organised%20themselves%20to%20protest%20against%20multiple%20issues%20like%20killings%20of%20innocents%20in%20Silger%20and%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20security%20forces%E2%80%99%20camps%20in%20Elmakonda.%20Though%20a%20retired%20IPS%20officer%20has%20attributed%20this%20development%20of%20democratic%20consensus%20to%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20camps%2C%20the%20voting%20pattern%20of%20the%20villagers%20suggests%20otherwise.%20Around%2026%25%20of%20votes%20in%20Silger%2C%2051%25%20of%20votes%20in%20Minpa%2C%20and%2091.5%25%20of%20votes%20in%20Elmagonda%20were%20cast%20in%20favour%20of%20Manish%20Kunjam%2C%20a%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20leader%20who%20has%20been%20active%20in%20anti-mining%20and%20democratic%20protests%20for%20decades%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%2046%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Bijapur%20district%2C%20another%20hotbed%20of%20the%20Maoist%20conflict%20in%20the%20South%20Bastar%20region%2C%20has%20voted%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections.%20Though%20the%20overall%20percentage%20has%20dipped%20by%202%25%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20multiple%20media%20reports%20have%20covered%20how%20Adivasis%20in%20Bijapur%20have%20participated%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20even%20after%20multiple%20threats%20by%20Maoists.%20About%20110%20schools%20that%20had%20been%20demolished%20were%20re-opened%20in%20Bijapur%20in%202021%20and%20restoration%20of%20health%20infrastructure%20followed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20read%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhasdeo-arand-deforestation-raises-questions-of-adivasi-justice-for-chhattisgarhs-first-tribal-cm%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EHasdeo%20Arand%20Deforestation%20Raises%20Questions%20of%20Adivasi%20Justice%20for%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20First%20Tribal%20CM%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20both%20the%20parties%20to%20this%20war%20have%20been%20ignoring%20this%20pro-democracy%20and%20pro-constitution%20voice%20of%20Adivasis%20that%20they%20have%20asserted%20by%20participating%20in%20electoral%20polls%20against%20all%20odds.%20The%20parties%20have%20deepened%20their%20maelstrom%20of%20violence%2C%20and%20caught%20between%20this%20violence%20are%20Adivasis%20and%20their%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChild%20rights%20violation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fsix-month-old-infant-killed-mother-injured-in-crossfire-between-security-forces-and-maoists-in-bastar%2Farticleshow%2F106457568.cms%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ea%20six-month-old%20infant%20in%20Bijapur%20district%E2%80%99s%20Mudvendi%20village%20was%20shot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20The%20security%20forces%20have%20previously%20asserted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20Maoist%20bullet%20that%20hit%20the%20infant%20but%20are%20now%20claiming%20that%20they%20acted%20in%20self-defence%20in%20response%20to%20Maoist%20firing.%20However%2C%20the%20villagers%20have%20been%20vehemently%20opposing%20the%20forces%E2%80%99%20claim%20and%20asserting%20that%20the%20firing%20was%20unprovoked.%20As%20per%20the%20villagers%2C%20the%20security%20forces%20had%20fired%20on%20the%20infant%20and%20there%20was%20no%20confrontation%20of%20Maoists%20with%20the%20forces.%20This%20incident%20has%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20already%20fragile%20relationship%20between%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20Adivasis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EForces%20were%20deployed%20in%20the%20region%20to%20secure%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20road%20that%20was%20built%20without%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20Gram%20Sabha%20in%20violation%20of%20PESA.%20It%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20huge%20trees%20of%20economic%20and%20cultural%20importance%20to%20Adivasis%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echhind%2C%20salfi%2C%20mahua%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20being%20cut.%20Adivasis%20of%20the%20region%20had%20gathered%20on%20December%2027%2C%202023%20to%20protest%20the%20felling%20of%20these%20trees.%20The%20villagers%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20a%20new%20security%20forces%20camp%20was%20about%20to%20be%20constructed%20in%20the%20village.%20The%20protest%20continued%20for%20three%20days%20and%20had%20been%20growing.%20Security%20forces%20had%20opened%20fire%20in%20the%20air%20to%20scare%20off%20the%20villagers.%20However%2C%20their%20counterparts%20stationed%20away%20from%20the%20location%20misunderstood%20these%20warning%20shots%20as%20firing%20by%20Maoists%20and%20started%20firing%20relentlessly%20which%20claimed%20the%20life%20of%20an%20infant%20girl.%20Hunga%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20village%20along%20with%20two%20other%20villagers%20had%20raised%20an%20alarm%20after%20which%20the%20firing%20was%20stopped.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20alleged%20that%20after%20realizing%20the%20blunder%20committed%2C%20the%20villagers%20were%20offered%20some%20cash%20and%20liquor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoni%20Sori%2C%20an%20Adivasi%20rights%20activist%2C%20has%20pointed%20out%20the%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20security%20forces%E2%80%99%20versions.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20claimed%20that%20two%20of%20their%20soldiers%20were%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20encounter%2C%20however%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20not%20released%20their%20details%20or%20photos%20yet.%20The%20infant%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Masa%20is%20also%20injured%20but%20the%20injury%20is%20not%20so%20severe%20that%20she%20needs%20to%20be%20hospitalized%20for%20long.%20She%20has%20been%20virtually%20imprisoned%20in%20Jagdalpur%20Dimrapal%20Medical%20College%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20treatment%20and%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20meet%20anyone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvocate%20Bela%20Bhatia%20was%20present%20with%20the%20villagers%20who%20were%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Bijapur%20Collectorate%20on%20January%2016%20to%20demand%20justice%20for%20the%20child.%20The%20villagers%20were%20stopped%20amid%20heavy%20deployment%20of%20forces%20before%20reaching%20the%20Collectorate.%20Bhatia%20told%20the%20local%20media%20how%20the%20administration%20was%20reluctant%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20about%20the%20incident.%20She%20further%20discussed%20the%20legal%20aspects%20and%20apathy%20displayed%20by%20the%20administration%20in%20this%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdivasis%20walking%20to%20participate%20in%20democratic%20protests%20against%20the%20killing%20have%20alleged%20police%20firing%20at%20unarmed%20and%20innocent%20protestors%20while%20they%20were%20crossing%20a%20hill%20in%20Belam%20Gatta%20region%20of%20Bijapur%2C%20killing%20three%20people%20on%20January%2020%2C%202024.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20alleged%20that%20two%20out%20of%20the%20three%20slain%20are%20children.%20Security%20forces%20have%20alleged%20an%20encounter%20with%20Maoists%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths.%20Advocate%20Bela%20Bhatia%20who%20has%20been%20to%20the%20village%20has%20alleged%20that%20three%20killed%20are%20Soni%20Markam%2C%20Nagi%20Punem%20and%20Kosa%20Karam.%20Kosa%20was%20a%20farmer%20and%20a%20father%20to%20five%20children%20and%20Soni%20and%20Nagi%20were%2014%20and%2015%20year%20old%20children.%20The%20villagers%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20in%20Basaguda%20Police%20Station%20in%20Bijapur%20on%20January%2024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20read%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fphoto-essay-dalits-adivasis-in-odishas-tijimali-fight-back-vedantas-mining-bid%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20Photos%3A%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Tijmali%20Push%20Back%20Against%20Vedanta%E2%80%99s%20Mining%20Bid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%208-year-old%20girl%20was%20also%20severely%20injured%20in%20an%20IED%20blast%20in%20the%20Cherpal-Palnar%20region%20of%20Bijapur%20district%20on%C2%A0%20January%205%2C%202024.%20The%20IED%20was%20planted%20by%20Maoists%20to%20target%20security%20personnel.%20The%20child%20was%20studying%20in%20the%20third%20grade%20at%20a%20government%20residential%20school%20in%20Bijapur.%20She%20was%20walking%20back%20to%20her%20village%20with%20her%20mother%20after%20completing%20some%20errands%20in%20the%20nearby%20town%20when%20the%20incident%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20these%20severe%20violations%20of%20child%20rights%20by%20both%20parties%20of%20war%20in%20armed%20conflict%20zones%20come%20after%20the%20UN%20has%20certified%20the%20state%20to%20have%20implemented%20all%20their%20recommendations%20to%20secure%20child%20rights%20during%20armed%20conflicts%20in%20a%20report%20released%20by%20them%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchildrenandarmedconflict.un.org%2Fdocument%2Fsecretary-general-annual-report-on-children-and-armed-conflict-2%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20state%20has%20no%20more%20armed%20conflict%20affecting%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20high%20time%20that%20the%20state%20undertakes%20efforts%20to%20secure%20Adivasis%20and%20their%20children%20from%20becoming%20collateral%20damage.%20The%20lack%20of%20accountability%20displayed%20by%20the%20state%20in%20these%20regions%20fosters%20a%20culture%20of%20impunity%2C%20where%20security%20forces%20operate%20without%20their%20actions%20being%20questioned.%20The%20failure%20to%20address%20these%20grievances%20of%20the%20native%20Adivasis%20of%20these%20regions%20has%20eroded%20the%20trust%20between%20the%20villagers%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20fuelling%20resentment%20among%20them%20and%20exacerbating%20the%20current%20crisis.%20Addressing%20these%20unresolved%20cases%20is%20crucial%20for%20rebuilding%20trust%20and%20fostering%20a%20sense%20of%20justice%20and%20democracy%20within%20the%20community.%20Maoists%20further%20exploit%20this%20distrust%20to%20garner%20sympathy%20and%20support%20from%20the%20aggrieved%20population%2C%20complicating%20efforts%20to%20bring%20stability%20to%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20needs%20to%20understand%20how%20positively%20the%20Adivasis%20dwelling%20in%20the%20sensitive%20regions%20of%20Sukma%20and%20Bijapur%20have%20responded%20to%20its%20initiative%20of%20restoring%20the%20education%20and%20health%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20sensitive%20regions.%20This%20is%20evident%20by%20their%20robust%20participation%20in%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20needs%20to%20now%20focus%20on%20creating%20more%20job%20opportunities%20in%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20and%20health%20sectors%20for%20the%20local%20Adivasi%20population%20and%20initiate%20peace%20talks.%20They%20should%20stop%20the%20violation%20of%20FRA%20and%20PESA%20through%20large-scale%20militarisation%20of%20the%20region.The%20Maoist%20leadership%20should%20hear%20the%20pro-democratic%20and%20pro-constitution%20voices%2