position%20in%20Punjab%20Assembly%2C%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20get%20together%2C%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote%20is%20going%20to%20shift%2C%20either%20to%20the%20BJP%20or%20to%20the%20Akali%20Dal.%20How%20can%20we%20relinquish%20our%20position%3F%20Congress%20is%20on%20the%20comeback%20train.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20will%20finish%20our%20existence.%20We%20have%20to%20preserve%20our%20vote%20bank%2C%20and%20build%20on%20it.%20This%20is%20much%20better%20for%20both%20(Congress%20and%20AAP)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bajwa%20said%20that%20the%20seats%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20win%20will%20remain%20with%20the%20anti-BJP%20Opposition%20bloc%20anyway.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20fighting%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20and%20outside%20it.%20Every%20day%2C%20the%20main%20opposition%20is%20coming%20from%20the%20Congress.%20We%20are%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Punjab%20against%20them.%20How%20do%20you%20think%20we%20can%20sit%20on%20the%20same%20stage%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20this%20is%20not%20his%20stand%20alone.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20Congress%20worker%20(feels%20the%20same).%20Our%20general%20secretary%20has%20been%20holding%20meetings%20with%20Congress%20workers%2C%20block%20president%2C%20district%20president%2C%20MLAs%20and%20former%20MLAs%2C%20MPs%20and%20former%20MPs%2C%20state%20party%20presidents.%2099.9%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20with%20folded%20hands%20have%20suggested%20that%20we%20would%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20AAP.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20Mr%20Mann%2C%20he%20has%20made%20our%20job%20a%20little%20easier.%20This%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20denied%20that%20such%20statements%20were%20part%20of%20bargaining%20tactics.%20%26quot%3BIf%20our%20votes%20shift%20to%20another%20party%2C%20they%20won't%20come%20back%20during%20the%202027%20Assembly%20polls.%20We%20have%20already%20seen%20such%20experiments%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Delhi.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20we%20helped%20these%20AAP%20guys%20to%20form%20their%20government%20in%202014.%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20are%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen.%20We%20don't%20want%20a%20similar%20situation%20in%20Punjab%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20yesterday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mamata-banerjee-aap-says-no-alliance-with-congress-in-punjab-4922817%5C%22%3Esparked%20a%20buzz%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20announcing%20that%20AAP%20is%20working%20on%20finalising%20candidates%20for%20all%2013%20Punjab%20seats.%20Soon%20after%2C%20MP%20and%20Punjab%20co-incharge%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20played%20down%20the%20remarks%20and%20said%20the%20final%20decision%20was%20yet%20to%20be%20taken.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20new.%20Punjab%20unit%20had%20been%20saying%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20contesting%20alone.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20local%20unit%20of%20Congress%2C%20they%20too%20say%20that%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20forge%20an%20alliance.%20So%2C%20local%20units%20have%20their%20own%20aspirations.%20The%20final%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20coordination%20committee%2C%20seat-sharing%20committee%20and%20the%20High%20Command.%20Let's%20wait%20for%20it.%20The%20sooner%20it%20is%20done%2C%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann's%20remarks%20had%20come%20shortly%20after%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20suffered%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-relations-with-congress-mamata-banerjee-to-fight-alone-in-bengal-4922151%5C%22%3Esetback%20in%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supremo%20ruling%20out%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20too%2C%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20has%20been%20opposed%20t