t%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E19.8%20Overthrow%20or%20wilful%20act%20of%20fielder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20boundary%20results%20from%20an%20overthrow%20or%20from%20the%20wilful%20act%20of%20a%20fielder%2C%20the%20runs%20scored%20shall%20be%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eany%20runs%20for%20penalties%20awarded%20to%20either%20side%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eand%20the%20allowance%20for%20the%20boundary%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eand%20the%20runs%20completed%20by%20the%20batters%2C%20together%20with%20the%20run%20in%20progress%20if%20they%20had%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ealready%20crossed%20at%20the%20instant%20of%20the%20throw%20or%20act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsha%20Bhogle%2C%20the%20commentator%20during%20the%20incident%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20first%20Test%2C%20explained%20the%20matter%20on-air%20while%20also%20reminding%20former%20England%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Eoin%20Morgan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F833-eoin-morgan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EEoin%20Morgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20what%20was%20the%20case%20in%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20scenario%20that%20unfolded%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706173200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ffq89avu8_stokes-and-rehan-afp_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fwhy-england-were-awarded-5-runs-instead-of-6-despite-batters-running-double-before-overthrow-4-4929187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22England%20were%20initially%20awarded%206%20runs%2C%20for%20a%20double%20and%20an%20overthrow%204%20during%20the%20Day%201%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20India.%20But%2C%20later%20the%20runs%20were%20reduced%20to%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thai%20police%20to%20charge%20t