20Everyone's%20Ram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20easily%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20hour%20of%20triumph.%20Yet%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20sounding%20triumphant%20after%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%20He%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20political%20project%20or%20a%20trophy%20to%20be%20flaunted%20by%20his%20party.%20To%20ensure%20that%20the%20Ayodhya%20event%20was%20not%20an%20all-BJP%20show%20but%20a%20national%20event%2C%20senior%20ministers%20in%20the%20government%20such%20as%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20or%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20or%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20stayed%20away.%20They%20were%20seen%20offering%20prayers%20at%20various%20temples%20across%20India%20-%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Kanchipuram%20and%20Cuttack.%20Encomiums%20were%20showered%20on%20Modi%20by%20a%20seer%20who%20hailed%20him%20for%20maintaining%20the%20rigours%20of%20an%2011-day%20fast%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20when%20three-day%20abstention%20would%20have%20sufficed.%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20joined%20in%20to%20call%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Btapasvi%26quot%3B.%20Minutes%20after%20the%20consecration%2C%20Modi%20called%20for%20restrained%20celebrations%2C%20saying%20it%20wasn't%20just%20%26quot%3Ba%20moment%20of%20celebration%26quot%3B%20but%20also%20a%20moment%20that%20signified%20%26quot%3Bthe%20maturity%20of%20Indian%20society%26quot%3B.%20The%20Ram%20Mandir%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20was%20not%20about%20victory%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Balso%20about%20humility%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20humility%20and%20the%20need%20for%20it%2C%20Modi%20warned%20that%20many%20nations%20had%20faced%20great%20difficulties%20in%20achieving%20success%20in%20the%20process%20of%20trying%20to%20untangle%20history.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20situation%20had%20often%20become%20more%20challenging%20than%20before.%20However%2C%20he%20lauded%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20country%20had%20%26quot%3Buntangled%20this%20knot%20of%20history%20with%20seriousness%20and%20sensitivity%26quot%3B.%20It%20indicates%2C%20he%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20our%20future%20will%20be%20much%20more%20beautiful%20than%20our%20past%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fmqcbfpug_ram-temple-ayodhya-ani_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20from%20the%20precincts%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20PM%20Modi%20outlined%20his%20concept%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20and%20shared%20that%20he%20discovered%20Ram%20as%20the%20unifier%20of%20India%20is%20central%20to%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20nation.%20He%20had%20found%20that%20Ram%20is%20revered%20from%20Sagar%20(South)%20to%20Saryu%20(North)%20during%20his%20travels%20across%20the%20country%20as%20part%20of%20his%2011-day%20rituals.%20%26quot%3BToday%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20not%20just%20the%20idol%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20has%20been%20infused%20with%20life.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20life-infusion%20of%20unbreakable%20faith%20in%20Indian%20culture%20as%20represented%20by%20Shri%20Ram.%20Today%2C%20this%20resolution%20has%20taken%20a%20concrete%20shape%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20was%20reaching%20out%20to%20all%20Indians.%20In%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20exclusion.%20He%20emphasised%20that%20Ram%20belonged%20to%20all.%20He%20made%20this%20point%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20RSS%20chief.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20reachout%20to%20Muslims%20seemed%20convincing%20and%20was%20appreciated%20by%20the%20community.%20In%20fact%2C%20former%20AMU%20chancellor%20Zameeruddin%20Shah%20went%20on%20record%20to%20welcome%20PM%20Modi's%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BRam%20belongs%20to%20all%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%20He%20accepted%20that%20%26quot%3BRam%20as%20an%20entity%20not%20only%20belonged%20to%20India%20but%20also%20to%20South%20Asia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20backdrop%2C%20as%20PM%20Modi%20subtly%20outlined%20his%20concept%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%20He%20urged%20everyone%20to%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%20to%20Ram%20Mandir%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20people%20to%20%26quot%3Brethink%20their%20perspective%26quot%3B.%20He%20explained%20how%20Ram%20is%20present%20in%20India's%20Constitution%2C%20in%20its%20first%20copy.%20It%20is%20another%20matter%20that%20legal%20battles%20over%20the%20existence%20of%20Ram%20had%20gone%20on%20for%20decades.%20Describing%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnation%20rising%26quot%3B%20by%20breaking%20the%20mentality%20of%20colonial%20slavery%2C%20he%20underscored%20its%20importance%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bunifier%26quot%3B.%20He%20possibly%20acquired%20this%20perspective%20when%20he%20visited%20places%20linked%20to%20Lord%20Ram%20as%20part%20of%20his%2011-day%20anushthan.%20Listening%20to%20various%20versions%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20must%20have%20made%20him%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20Ram%20that%20unites%20the%20North%20and%20the%20South.%20His%20Ramayana%20trail%20of%20the%20Panchavati%20Dham%20in%20Nashik%20(Maharashtra)%2C%20the%20sacred%20Triprayar%20Temple%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Lepakshi%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Ranganathaswamy%20Temple%20in%20Srirangam%2C%20Shri%20Ramanathaswamy%20Temple%20in%20Rameshwaram%2C%20or%20Dhanushkodi%2C%20were%20a%20learning%20experience%2C%20by%20Modi's%20own%20admission.%20Giving%20a%20context%20to%20Modi's%20move%20to%20rely%20on%20Ram%20to%20unify%20people%2C%20Tughlak%20editor%20S%20Gurumurthy%20explained%20that%20PM%20Modi%20was%20possibly%20only%20trying%20to%20follow%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20and%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20who%20expounded%20the%20spiritual%20nationalism%20of%20people%20by%20symbolically%20identifying%20Ram%20and%20Ram%20Bhajan.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20power%20which%20he%20reposed%20in%20Ram%2C%20and%20said%20Swaraj%20means%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gurumurthy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20is%20driving%20Modi%20to%20push%20the%20Ram%20temple%20as%20a%20mainstream%20project%20that%20is%20acceptable%20to%20all%3F%C2%A0%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20did%20briefly%20recall%20the%20years%20of%20fear%20mongering%20over%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20how%20there%20were%20always%20some%20who%20talked%20about%20unrest%20if%20the%20temple%20were%20to%20be%20built.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20people%20failed%20to%20understand%20the%20purity%20of%20India's%20social%20sentiment.%20The%20construction%20of%20this%20temple%20of%20Ramlalla%20is%20also%20a%20symbol%20of%20peace%2C%20patience%2C%20harmony%2C%20and%20coordination%20in%20the%20Indian%20society.%20We%20are%20seeing%20that%20this%20construction%20is%20not%20igniting%20any%20fire%2C%20but%20rather%20it%20is%20giving%20birth%20to%20energy.%20The%20Ram%20temple%20has%20brought%20inspiration%20for%20every%20section%20of%20society%20to%20move%20towards%20a%20brighter%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Modi%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20rebrand%20Ram%20as%20everyone's%20Ram%2C%20an%20all-encompassing%20Ram%20--%20a%20Ram%20who%20is%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20universe.%20It%20was%20the%20pitch%20and%20thrust%20of%20his%20address.%20%26quot%3BRam%20is%20not%20fire%2C%20Ram%20is%20energy.%20Ram%20is%20not%20a%20dispute%2C%20Ram%20is%20the%20resolution.%20Ram%20is%20not%20only%20ours%2C%20Ram%20is%20for%20everyone...%20This%20is%20not%20just%20a%20divine%20temple.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20a%20temple%20of%20India's%20vision%2C%20philosophy%2C%20and%20direction.%20It%20is%20a%20temple%20of%20national%20consciousness%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Ram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20moving%20beyond%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20PM%20Modi%C2%A0%20touched%20on%20other%20achievements%20that%20the%20country%20has%20witnessed%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20From%20hoisting%20the%20flag%20on%20the%20Moon's%20South%20Pole%20to%20successfully%20conducting%20Mission%20Aditya%20by%20traveling%2015%20lakh%20km%20to%20the%20Sun%2C%20to%20waving%20the%20flag%20of%20Tejas%20in%20the%20sky%20and%20Vikrant%20in%20the%20sea.%20He%20urged%20young%20Indians%20to%20be%20proud%20of%20their%20heritage.%20%26quot%3BThis%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20will%20be%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20magnificent%20India%2C%20to%20the%20development%20of%20India!%26quot%3B%20Inarguably%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20has%20brought%20a%20big%20infra%20push%20to%20Ayodhya%20and%20adjoining%20areas%2C%20beginning%20with%20it%20a%20national%20four-lane%20highway%2C%20an%20international%20airport%20and%20a%20cruise%20across%20river%20Saryu.%C2%A0%20Even%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20such%20facilities%20were%20unthinkable.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706169420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhr8a4smo_narendra-modi-ani_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-pm-modi-wants-to-rebrand-ram-as-everyones-ram-4929067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20easily%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20hour%20of%20triumph.%20Yet%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20sounding%20triumphant%20after%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%20He%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20temple%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20political%20project%20or%20a%20trophy%20to%20be%20flaunted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-pm-modi-wants-to-rebrand-ram-as-everyones-ram-4929067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justice%20in%20India%20Requires%20Inspiration%20from%20the%20Tricolour%2C%20Not%20Temple%20Dhwajas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%2070%20years%20old%20and%20have%20spent%20around%2040%20meaningful%20years%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20and%20am%20today%20anguished%20by%20the%20blurring%20of%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20public%20places%2C%20by%20people%20who%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20is%20not%20intended%20as%20a%20personal%20attack%20on%20anyone%2C%20but%20merely%20an%20effort%20to%20place%20before%20a%20a%20reasonable%20person%20some%20observations%20on%20the%20subtle%20use%20of%20images%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20the%20general%20public%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20government%20which%20is%20constantly%20jostling%20for%20more%20space.%20And%20a%20government%20which%2C%20like%20the%20British%20Raj%2C%20has%20learnt%20and%20is%20methodically%20polishing%20the%20art%20of%20divide%20and%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20the%20claim%20of%20an%20elected%20government%20to%20being%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%20but%20that%20does%20not%20negate%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20judiciary%20as%20the%20final%20arbiter%20of%20issues%20concerning%20the%20nation.%20Being%20at%20such%20a%20central%20place%2C%20its%20importance%20can%20neither%20be%20undermined%20nor%20compared%20with%20other%20organs%20of%20the%20state.%20Each%20organ%20has%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20its%20own%20space%20but%20in%20conflict%20situations%20it%20is%20the%20judiciary%20which%20under%20the%20scheme%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20the%20last%20say.%20There%20is%20no%20show%20of%20strength%20here%2C%20no%20flexing%20of%20muscles.%20This%20is%20the%20way%20of%20life%20put%20together%20by%20mature%20and%20learned%20minds%20after%20quality%20debates%20by%20way%20of%20a%20written%20Constitution.%20And%20it%20is%20because%20of%20this%20%E2%80%93%20when%20we%20have%20pledged%20ourselves%20a%20secular%20nation%20committed%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20that%20justice%20must%20be%20done%20and%20%3Cem%3Eseen%20to%20have%20been%20done.%3C%2Fem%3E%20This%20is%20precisely%20why%20images%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20because%20of%20this%20that%20many%20find%20the%20picture%20of%20five%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20%E2%80%98celebrating%E2%80%99%20their%20Ayodhya%20judgment%20disturbing%20and%20ask%20whether%20it%20truly%20fits%20in%20with%20our%20constitutional%20values.%20For%20the%20first%20question%20which%20comes%20to%20mind%20when%20looking%20at%20that%20photograph%20is%20this%20%E2%80%94%20What%20was%20there%20to%20celebrate%20about%3F%20Was%20it%20a%20personal%20victory%20for%20the%20five%20judges%20as%20final%20arbiter%20of%20a%20long%20pending%20dispute%3F%20Surely%20for%20a%20judge%2C%20every%20order%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20her%20or%20his%20judicial%20acumen.%20So%20the%20Ayodhya%20judgment%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20how%20politically%20important%20for%20some%20%E2%80%93%20should%20have%20been%20seen%20as%20just%20another%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F09194806%2F2019_11img09_Nov_2019_PTI11_9_2019_000298B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F09194806%2F2019_11img09_Nov_2019_PTI11_9_2019_000298B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F09194806%2F2019_11img09_Nov_2019_PTI11_9_2019_000298B-300x236.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F09194806%2F2019_11img09_Nov_2019_PTI11_9_2019_000298B-1024x804.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-412147%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22942%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20group%20photo%20of%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%20(C)%20flanked%20by%20(L-R)%20Justice%20Ashok%20Bhushan%2C%20Justice%20Sharad%20Arvind%20Bobde%2C%20Justice%20Dhananjaya%20Y%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20S%20Abdul%20Nazeer%20after%20they%20delivered%20the%20verdict%20on%20Ayodhya%20land%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20ordinary%20mortals%2C%20judges%20are%20averse%20to%20being%20examined%20by%20an%20external%20body%20and%20therefore%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20hold%20chief%20justices%E2%80%99%20conferences%20and%20set%20down%20norms%20of%20behaviour%20for%20themselves.%20In%20April%202000%2C%20a%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20Vienna%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20where%20judges%20%E2%80%93%20including%20participants%20from%20India%20%E2%80%93%20recognised%20the%20need%20for%20a%20code%20against%20which%20the%20conduct%20of%20judicial%20officers%20may%20be%20measured.%20In%20preparing%20a%20draft%20code%20of%20judicial%20conduct%2C%20several%20existing%20codes%20and%20international%20instruments%20were%20studied%20and%20then%20the%20Bangalore%20Draft%20Code%20of%20Judicial%20Conduct%2C%202001%20was%20adopted%20by%20the%20judicial%20group%20on%20strengthening%20judicial%20integrity%2C%20at%20the%20Round%20Table%20meeting%20of%20Chief%20Justices%20held%20at%20the%20Peace%20Palace%20in%20The%20Hague%20on%20November%2025-26%2C%202002.%20Thus%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unodc.org%2Fpdf%2Fcrime%2Fcorruption%2Fjudicial_group%2FBangalore_principles.pdf%5C%22%3EBangalore%20Principles%20of%20Judicial%20Conduct%2C%202002%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20into%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preamble%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20confidence%20in%20the%20judicial%20system%20and%20in%20the%20moral%20authority%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20judiciary%20was%20of%20the%20utmost%20importance%20in%20a%20modern%20democratic%20society%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20accepted%20that%20it%20was%20essential%20that%20%E2%80%9Cjudges%2C%20individually%20and%20collectively%2C%20respect%20and%20honour%20judicial%20office%20as%20a%20public%20trust%20and%20strive%20to%20enhance%20and%20maintain%20confidence%20in%20the%20judicial%20system%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Must%20Justice%20Have%20a%20Colour%3F%C2%A0%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmust-justice-have-a-colour%5C%22%3EMust%20Justice%20Have%20a%20Colour%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20six%20ethical%20principles%20were%20laid%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EValue%201%20was%20the%20value%20of%20Independence%2C%20it%20being%20%E2%80%9Ca%20pre-requisite%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20a%20fundamental%20guarantee%20of%20a%20fair%20trial%E2%80%9D.%20A%20judge%20was%20therefore%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuphold%20and%20exemplify%20judicial%20independence%20in%20both%20its%20individual%20and%20institutional%20aspects%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Principle%20of%20Integrity%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20judge%20shall%20ensure%20that%20his%20or%20her%20conduct%20is%20above%20reproach%20in%20the%20view%20of%20a%20%3Cu%3Ereasonable%20observer%3C%2Fu%3E%20and%20his%20%3Cu%3Ebehaviour%3C%2Fu%3E%20and%20%3Cu%3Econduct%3C%2Fu%3E%20must%20%3Cu%3Ereaffirm%3C%2Fu%3E%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%9D.%20It%20clearly%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20imagery%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CJustice%20must%20not%20merely%20be%20done%20but%20must%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Principle%20of%20the%20Propriety%2C%20it%20said%20while%20a%20judge%2C%20like%20any%20other%20citizen%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Centitled%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20belief%2C%20association%20and%20assembly%2C%20but%20in%20exercising%20such%20rights%2C%20a%20judge%20shall%20always%20conduct%20himself%20or%20herself%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20as%20to%20preserve%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20judicial%20office%20and%20the%20impartiality%20and%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20the%20above%20principles%2C%20judges%20%E2%80%93%20while%20making%20visits%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20religious%20places%20%E2%80%93%20are%20obliged%20to%20keep%20their%20visits%20private%20and%20forbid%20any%20public%20display.%20This%20helps%20reaffirms%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20secular%20character%20of%20a%20judge%2C%20especially%20when%20she%20or%20he%20is%20called%20upon%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20issues%20of%20faith.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20semblance%20of%20impartiality%20and%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%20is%20maintained.%20This%20restraint%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance%20because%20of%20the%20image%20of%20justice%20not%20only%20being%20done%20but%20shown%20to%20have%20been%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stressing%20that%20optics%20are%20important%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20age%20of%20media%20penetration%20and%20its%20tendency%20to%20amplify%20issues%2C%20let%20us%20examine%20the%20recent%20visit%20of%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%20to%20the%20Somnath%20Temple%20in%20Dwarka%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20offering%20prayers%20to%20the%20deity%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20in%20a%20yellow-orange%20kurta%20which%20many%20saw%20%E2%80%93%20wrongly%20or%20rightly%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20colour%20chosen%20to%20promote%20the%20interests%20of%20a%20dominant%20political%20party.%20There%20is%20plenty%20of%20scope%20for%20giving%20the%20CJI%20the%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20on%20this%20score.%20He%20may%20have%20chosen%20the%20colour%20of%20his%20liking%20deliberately%20or%20accidentally.%20Whatever%20was%20done%20was%20done%20in%20his%20personal%20capacity%20as%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20not%20as%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India.%20As%20per%20judicial%20principles%2C%20a%20judge%20may%20be%20evaluated%20on%20the%20quality%20or%20slant%20of%20judgments%20he%20authors.%20In%20other%20matters%2C%20he%20is%20an%20ordinary%20citizen%20entitled%20to%20a%20private%20space%20and%20even%20as%20an%20occupant%20of%20public%20trust%20he%20is%20well%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20optics%20are%20important%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%20and%20one%20must%20tread%20cautiously.%20It%20is%20easy%20for%20people%20to%20connect%20images%20together%20and%20form%20unhealthy%20opinions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20'Is%20the%20CJI%20Wrong%20About%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20to%20Visit%20Hindu%20Temples%20in%20Saffron%20Robes%3F'%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkaran-thapar-cji-dy-chandrachud-ramachandra-guha%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Is%20the%20CJI%20Wrong%20About%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20to%20Visit%20Hindu%20Temples%20in%20Saffron%20Robes%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20for%20myself%2C%20what%20was%20disturbing%20to%20me%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-invokes-dhwaja-on-temples-to-serve-as-inspiration-for-courts-draws-attention%5C%22%3Ethe%20speech%20the%20CJI%20gave%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%20to%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20officers%20in%20his%20official%20capacity.%20The%20exact%20quote%20of%20the%20speech%20goes%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20inspired%20this%20morning%20by%20the%20Dhwaja%20at%20Dwarakadishi%20temple%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Dhwaja%20I%20saw%20at%20Jagannathpuri.%20But%20look%20at%20the%20universality%20of%20the%20tradition%20in%20our%20nation%2C%20which%20binds%20all%20of%20us%20together.%20But%20this%20Dhwaja%20has%20a%20special%20meaning%20for%20us.%20And%20that%20meaning%20which%20the%20Dhwaja%20gives%20us%20is%20that%20there%20is%20some%20unifying%20force%20above%20all%20of%20us%20as%20lawyers%2C%20as%20citizens%20and%20that%20unifying%20force%20is%20our%20humanity%20which%20is%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20by%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20be%20inspired%20by%20the%20ideals%20of%20these%20great%20temples%20which%20dot%20the%20landscape%20of%20Gujarat%E2%80%A6the%20district%20court%20lawyers%20have%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Dhwaja%20of%20Justice%20will%20keep%20flying%20in%20the%20generations%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20concerns%20as%20a%20reasonable%20observer%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20line%20of%20the%20speech%20emphasising%20one%E2%80%99s%20religion%20in%20a%20secular%20country%20by%20a%20person%20holding%20such%20a%20high%20office%20is%20bound%20to%20send%20an%20unsettling%20message%20to%20the%20people.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20has%20the%20CJI%20as%20a%20repository%20of%20public%20trust%2C%20enhanced%20public%20confidence%20in%20the%20moral%20authority%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20its%20adherence%20to%20the%20Bangalore%20Principles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20says%20%3Cem%3Edhwaj%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20special%20meaning%20for%20us%2C%20I%20wondered%20who%20this%20%E2%80%98us%E2%80%99%20is%3F%20As%20the%20highest%20officer%20of%20the%20judiciary%20of%20a%20secular%20country%2C%20was%20he%20speaking%20just%20about%20the%2079.8%25%20who%20are%20Hindus%3F%20Or%20also%20about%20the%2014.2%25%20Muslims%2C%201.7%25%20Sikhs%2C%202.3%25%20Christians%20and%20other%20faiths%20and%20the%2025.2%25%20Dalits%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20regularly%20barred%20entry%20in%20Hindu%20temples%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20could%20a%20pure%20Hindu%20Icon%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Ed%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehwaja%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20a%20temple%2C%20be%20an%20icon%20of%20universality%20and%20of%20the%20binding%20nature%20of%20tradition%3F%20For%20a%20pious%20Hindu%20believer%2C%20the%20words%20would%20sound%20very%20innocuous%2C%20but%20that%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20case%20for%20a%20non-Hindu%20or%20even%20for%20a%20Shaivite%20or%20an%20atheist%20among%20the%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20further%20disconcerted%20and%20disappointed%20when%20the%20CJI%20went%20on%20to%20prod%20his%20listeners%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20judicial%20officers%20who%20were%20undoubtedly%20of%20diverse%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20that%20they%20be%20inspired%20by%20the%20temples%20that%20dot%20Gujarat.%20Was%20this%20a%20result%20of%20the%20proverbial%20pushback%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20government%3F%20Did%20a%20constitutional%20authority%20blatantly%20disregard%20and%20disrespect%20the%20secular%20character%20of%20our%20sacrosanct%20Constitution%3F%20It%20is%20not%20understandable%20how%20a%20person%20of%20his%20rank%2C%20acting%20as%20caretaker%20of%20an%20institution%2C%20constitutionally%20tasked%20with%20being%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20every%20citizen%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%20could%20have%20identified%20his%20personal%20religion%20with%20that%20of%20the%20institution%20of%20which%20he%20is%20only%20a%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%2C%20what%20I%20expected%20the%20CJI%20%E2%80%93%20a%20person%20of%20impeccable%20education%20and%20learning%20%E2%80%93%20to%20say%20after%20his%20temple%20visit%20was%20that%20the%20sole%20unifying%20%3Cem%3Edhwaj%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20our%20country%20is%20the%20tricolour%20and%20that%20it%20is%20our%20public%20duty%20not%20only%20to%20hoist%20it%2C%20but%20also%20keep%20it%20flying%20proudly%20over%20our%20heads.%20Thus%2C%20faith%20would%20have%20triumphed%20over%20rituals%2C%20the%20principles%20of%20our%20rule%20book%20reaffirmed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20souls%20of%20the%20framers%20of%20our%20Constitution%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanjana-prakash%5C%22%3EAnjana%20Prakash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20and%20practices%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706169125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%