0the%20Galapagos%20Islands%20to%20the%20Atlantic%2C%20Neeru%20Saluja%20has%20explored%20lesser-known%20places%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Neeru%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20clouds%20attracted%20me.%20Now%2C%20mind%20you%2C%20Jaipur%20is%20a%20dry%20state%20so%20there%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20too%20many%20of%20them.%20But%20whenever%20I%E2%80%99d%20spot%20one%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20find%20myself%20wondering%20where%20it%20would%20be%20heading%20next.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20very%20lucky%20to%20be%20able%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20while%20I%20was%20stuck%20in%20bed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neeru%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20was%20a%20stroke%20of%20luck%20one%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20for%20granted%2C%20thought%20little%20Neeru.%20And%20today%2C%20almost%20six%20decades%20later%2C%20she%20believes%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20one%20horizon%20to%20the%20next%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20hour%20(the%20duration%20of%20the%20interview)%20hardly%20suffices%20to%20hear%20all%20of%20Neeru%E2%80%99s%20tales%20about%20her%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eescapades%20around%20the%20globe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20each%20new%20country%2C%20comes%20a%20new%20story%2C%20a%20new%20twist%20and%20a%20new%20learning.%20Naturally%2C%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20pick%20a%20favourite.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20trip%20is%20special%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20if%20she%20had%20to%20pick%20one%20that%20taught%20her%20the%20most%2C%20she%20says%20it%20would%20be%20her%20first%20solo%20adventure%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Christmas%20cruise%20through%20Europe%20in%202014.%20The%20view%20was%20glorious%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20Neeru%20cherished%20the%20trip%20